            <li>Personalized ads</li>
            <li>Proactively engage customers</li>
            <li>Dont make users wait on hold for the next available operator, smart bots can answer their questions and help them with their needs with a faster better experience</li>
            <li>improve your customer satisfaction bots never get tired, always respond appropriately, can have thousands of conversations at once and are available 24/7.</li>
            <li>One time investment that helps reduce staff requirements, answering simple questions and passing more complex questions to actual humans</li>
            <li>Get more satisfied customers. Chatbots are always in a good mood, are always polite no matter how mean the customer is and can even be trained to respond in the language of the customer</li>
            <li>Reduce repetitive work</li>
